    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Agricultural complexes used for growing lemons. Composed of high perimiter walls and interconnected pillars often with with movable shutters, opened or closed in correspondence to warm and cold weather. Limonaie are chiefly associated with the area surrounding Lake Garda in Northern Italy.</Note_Text>
